          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Reward Work Act </b></p> <p>This bill prohibits issuers from purchasing their own securities on a national exchange. The bill also requires one-third of&nbsp;an issuer's&nbsp;board of directors&nbsp;to be&nbsp;elected by employees in order&nbsp;for the issuer to be allowed&nbsp;to register securities. </p>]]></text>
